<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q27_v12" title="Q27_v12" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>El trinomio 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>25</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      se quiere escribir como producto de dos binomios de la forma (x + a)(x + b). Para que la factorización sea correcta, a y b deben cumplir simultáneamente que su suma es 10 y su producto es 25.
    </p>
    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes descomposiciones en factores es coherente con este trinomio?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
            </m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Esta opción es <strong>(x + 5)(x + 5)</strong>, por lo que <strong>a = 5</strong> y <strong>b = 5</strong>. Entonces su suma es <strong>5 + 5 = 10</strong> y su producto es <strong>5 × 5 = 25</strong>. Además, al desarrollar se obtiene <strong>x² + 10x + 25</strong>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Aquí <strong>a = 2</strong> y <strong>b = 8</strong>. Su suma es <strong>2 + 8 = 10</strong>, pero su producto es <strong>2 × 8 = 16</strong>, no <strong>25</strong>. Por eso, al desarrollar resulta <strong>x² + 10x + 16</strong>, que no coincide con el trinomio dado.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Aquí <strong>a = 1</strong> y <strong>b = 25</strong>. Su producto es <strong>1 × 25 = 25</strong>, pero su suma es <strong>1 + 25 = 26</strong>, no <strong>10</strong>. Por eso, al desarrollar resulta <strong>x² + 26x + 25</strong>, que no coincide con el trinomio dado.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Aquí <strong>a = 3</strong> y <strong>b = 7</strong>. Su suma es <strong>3 + 7 = 10</strong>, pero su producto es <strong>3 × 7 = 21</strong>, no <strong>25</strong>. Por eso, al desarrollar resulta <strong>x² + 10x + 21</strong>, que no coincide con el trinomio dado.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Usar la forma general de la factorización</strong></p>
            <p>Si un trinomio se escribe como producto de dos binomios de la forma</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>al desarrollar se obtiene</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>b</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, para el trinomio dado, los valores <m:math><m:mi>a</m:mi></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:math> deben cumplir simultáneamente:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Revisar cada alternativa</strong></p>
            <p><em>Opción A:</em> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Cumple ambas condiciones.</p>
            <p><em>Opción B:</em> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              pero
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>No cumple el producto.</p>
            <p><em>Opción C:</em> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              pero
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>No cumple la suma.</p>
            <p><em>Opción D:</em> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              pero
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>21</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>No cumple el producto.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Verificar desarrollando la opción correcta</strong></p>
            <p>La opción A es</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Desarrollando:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>25</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>25</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Coincide exactamente con el trinomio del enunciado.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La descomposición coherente con el trinomio es la <strong>opción A</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>